<section class="py-16 md:py-24 px-5 md:px-10 bg-surface">
  <div class="text-center mb-12 fade-up">
    <div class="font-en text-sm text-primary tracking-[3px] uppercase mb-2.5">Our Advantage</div>
    <h3 class="font-en text-[28px] md:text-[38px] font-bold text-dark leading-snug"><em class="text-primary italic">OUR</em> Advantage</h3>
    <p class="text-[15px] text-muted mt-3.5">루미너스의 특장점 및 공지사항을 확인하세요!</p>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-[1100px] mx-auto fade-up">
    <div class="relative rounded-xl overflow-hidden min-h-[320px] flex items-end cursor-pointer group">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#2c2c2c] to-[#3a3a3a] group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"></div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/70 to-black/10 z-[1]"></div>
      <span class="absolute top-5 left-5 z-[2] bg-primary text-dark px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-bold tracking-wide rounded-sm">LUMINUS</span>
      <div class="relative z-[2] p-8 text-white w-full">
        <h4 class="text-[22px] font-bold mb-2">VIP MEMBERSHIP<br>특별한 혜택</h4>
        <p class="text-sm opacity-80">루미너스 VIP만을 위한 프리미엄 멤버십</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative rounded-xl overflow-hidden min-h-[320px] flex items-end cursor-pointer group">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#3a2a4a] to-[#5a3a6a] group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"></div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/70 to-black/10 z-[1]"></div>
      <span class="absolute top-5 left-5 z-[2] bg-primary text-dark px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-bold tracking-wide rounded-sm">LUMINUS</span>
      <div class="relative z-[2] p-8 text-white w-full">
        <h4 class="text-[22px] font-bold mb-2">최신 의료 장비<br>하이엔드 서비스</h4>
        <p class="text-sm opacity-80">검증된 최신 장비로 최상의 결과를 약속합니다</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="text-center mt-10 fade-up">
    <a href="#" class="inline-block py-3.5 px-10 border border-dark text-sm tracking-widest font-medium no-underline hover:bg-dark hover:text-white transition-colors">VIEW MORE</a>
  </div>
</section>
